# OWASP TorBot – required: set TORBOT_IMAGE (no official image published).
# Build from upstream (DedSecInside/TorBot) or use the Dockerfile in this stack once, push to your registry, then set below.

# TZ/locale: use shared.env (see documents/SHARED-RESOURCES.md)

# Required: image to use (no official image; build from upstream once and push, or use your registry)
# TORBOT_IMAGE=harbor.yourdomain.com/homelab/torbot:latest
